'''2012年[[MTV音乐录影带大奖|MTV音乐录影带大奖]]'''于2012年9月6日在[[美国|美国]][[加州|加州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]城区的[[斯台普斯中心|斯台普斯中心]]举行，颁奖典礼由[[凯文·哈特|凯文·哈特]]主持。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1685091/2012-video-music-awards-staples-center.jhtml?xrs=share_twitter|title=2012 Video Music Awards To Take Over Staples Center Show will air live from Los Angeles on Thursday, September 6, at 8 p.m. ET/PT.|last=Montgomery|first=James|date=15 May 2012|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|accessdate=2012-05-15|archive-date=2013-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516113049/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1685091/2012-video-music-awards-staples-center.jhtml?xrs=share_twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>提名于2012年7月31日公布，其中[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]与[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]各获得5项提名，其次是[[凯蒂·派瑞|凯蒂·派瑞]]与[[碧昂斯|碧昂斯]]各获得4项提名。<ref name="Nominees"/>

[[一世代|单向组合]]成为当晚最大赢家，包括“最佳新人奖”在内的3项提名全部获奖。[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]继[[2011年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2011年]]后又一次获得“年度音乐录影带大奖”。此外[[M.I.A.|M.I.A.]]与[[克里斯·布朗|克里斯·布朗]]也各获得两项大奖。<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/musicblog/2012/sep/07/mtv-video-music-awards-recap|title=MTV's video music awards keep the entertainment to a minimum|date=7 September 2012|work=Guardian UK|language=en-GB|accessdate=12 September 2012|archive-date=2013-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130218091019/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/musicblog/2012/sep/07/mtv-video-music-awards-recap|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://js.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2199629/MTV-VMAs-2012-One-Direction-Coldplay-sweep-board.html?openGraphAuthor=%2Fhome%2Fsearch.html%3Fs%3D%26authornamef%3DIona%2BKirby&videoPlayerURL=http%3A%2F%2Fc.brightcove.com%2Fservices%2Fviewer%2Ffederated_f9%3FisVid%3D1%26isUI%3D1%26publisherID%3D1418450360%26playerID%3D72484359001%26domain%3Dembed%26videoId%3D&hasBCVideo=true&BCVideoID=1827007531001|title=Rule Britannia! UK acts sweep the board at VMAs as One Direction and Coldplay take home trophies|date=7 September 2012|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=12 September 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822112341/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2199629/MTV-VMAs-2012-One-Direction-Coldplay-sweep-board.html?openGraphAuthor=%2Fhome%2Fsearch.html%3Fs%3D&authornamef=Iona+Kirby&videoPlayerURL=http%3A%2F%2Fc.brightcove.com%2Fservices%2Fviewer%2Ffederated_f9%3FisVid%3D1&isUI=1&publisherID=1418450360&playerID=72484359001&domain=embed&videoId=&hasBCVideo=true&BCVideoID=1827007531001|archive-date=2019-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/music-news/9527348/One-Direction-beat-Justin-Bieber-and-Rihanna-at-MTV-awards.html|title=One Direction beat Justin Bieber and Rihanna at MTV awards|date=7 September 2012|work=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=12 September 2012|archive-date=2018-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902220942/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/music-news/9527348/One-Direction-beat-Justin-Bieber-and-Rihanna-at-MTV-awards.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本届颁奖典礼是自2007年收视率最低的一届，其主要原因是主办方打破2004年以来（除2006年外）的惯例，将播出日期由星期日改为星期四。主办方MTV还将播出时间从晚9点提前至晚8点以避开[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]总统在2012年民主党全国大会的演讲，而这一时间对于MTV的较年轻的目标观众群来说过早。<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/news/ratings-dwindle-mtvs-annual-vma-show-215138851.html|title=Ratings dwindle for MTV's annual VMA show|date=11 September 2012|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=16 September 2012|archive-date=2015-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114193530/https://tv.yahoo.com/news/ratings-dwindle-mtvs-annual-vma-show-215138851.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

